README

4.22 First attempt at Django

changes:
* a Django project that can potentially host all parts of website
* an app named site_ver1 is installed(include index, login, and signup pages)
(done in Python 2.7.12)

lauch the Django server via:

cd Bluestream
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
if succeeded, python will output the url for the website to visit (usually http://127.0.0.1:8000/).



/////////////development notes/////////
Add an app to the Bluestream project:
go to /Bluestream/Bluestream/settings.py, add 'appname' to INSTALLED_APPS


